{"tid":306163,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"做熱狗水泥隊算唔算係世上最低賤既工種？","createTime":"2017-07-02T09:51:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T06:21:00.000Z","uid":32051,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"89da4f57434357fdcb703efd9e803fa79e8ca12d","tid":306163,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T09:51:09.000Z","msg":"五毛都叫有錢賺，反觀幫熱狗做水泥隊。<br />\n又要出錢，又要出力，仲要倒頭來俾鳩達屌返轉頭。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同你講一句你係<span style=\"color: violet;\">手足</span>，因為你只係幫緊你自己，就抹煞你所有付出，唔撚洗多謝你。<br />\n佢無欠你，反而你欠左佢，因為佢覺得佢畀左機會你幫佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你只係幫過佢既一條契弟<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係慘撚過做兵，做下等兵都最少得到女神說話鼓勵，對你好聲好氣。<br />\n做熱狗水泥隊，帶老母做野，水泥留言俾外人屌，做完仲要俾鳩達屌。<br />\n<br />\n熱狗水泥隊係咪真係世上最低賤既工種？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">其實熱狗已經係最低賤物種<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"fffa91468fbb5cf70a2366ac57fe4eca9e1fc58b","tid":306163,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T09:56:25.000Z","msg":"幫我地熱狗做野係光榮，做應份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4dc9a4f09a5851016ebb32b7235d499d040ebe7","tid":306163,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T10:00:54.000Z","msg":"其實法國佬都幾低賤下，幾十歲先入邪教仲要連女都冇理"},{"pid":"c1d1b2193dfdc75088f6238d3b05c50e79237b77","tid":306163,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T10:05:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/02/180503_2d282546c3c336982888b5d6c958aca4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F02%2F180503_2d282546c3c336982888b5d6c958aca4.jpg&h=d808c5ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4e862c13aed7fcc9a33e72a62b2a6deebc39004a","tid":306163,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T10:05:3