quote><br />\n12年我已經屌佢啦<br />\n人哋為佢好，佢就以為黃洋達當好人</blockquote><br />\n搞 抗爭 就係好需要呢d真心膠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你望下佢街站d人咩樣就知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n熱狗根本昆唔到智力正常既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n痴親埋去都係肥柒毒/奇撚怪既人<br />\neg 人妖羊 老師又中 堆三國人物 陳乂文等</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正常人有正常社交有咩可能埋到佢地堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n肯撚定好快俾佢地排走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd750f6c743277ff217817d62eacd349448c31a8","tid":306163,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:05:18.000Z","msg":"點解叫水泥隊"},{"pid":"e773919a8b3f2d231dbb52df33b0928f717033be","tid":306163,"uid":4384,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:28:04.000Z","msg":"做水泥隊有無得開課金link <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfe349415fadb6da9932b0952533b2984cb7def1","tid":306163,"uid":65649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T09:07:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解叫水泥隊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用海量既垃圾留言，信息阻你睇野（因為夾雜水泥隊極多既垃圾留言，要你睇件事既來龍去脈睇得好辛苦），等你件事失焦"},{"pid":"64a699ead722f016f75d87b1d437ca2d8476bb44","tid":306163,"uid":46527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T11:12:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/8z50j43f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F8z50j43f&h=2eae5787&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n350蚊一件，50件都係萬七蚊啫，信徒會俾嘅"},{"pid":"7a3d8f8d0abb6e64756dc5c8b25eff943c7c33e4","tid":306163,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T11:3